title: Once.Upon.a.Time.S06E00.WS.XviD-err0001.avi
description:
Once Upon a Time S06E00 - Evil Reigns Once More

A preview of the sixth season includes a look back at what the characters have experienced. Also: the show's executive producers are interviewed.

This episode aired on Sep 25, 2016. Like all of my releases to date, the source is an analog rip, in this case of an SD channel, so the quality is, at best, something like A7 V7. There are a few video glitches but nothing too serious
